lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Neon in my eyes, the night won’t let me breathe,
Shadows in the signal, calling out to me.
I keep moving forward, heartbeat like a drum,
If I stop for one second, then I’m already done.

[Chorus]
Don’t let me go, I’m holding on tonight,
Static in the dark, but I will find the light.
I won’t break, I won’t fade, I won’t be the one they catch,
I’m running through the storm — and I’m never looking back.
